data.description: CUSTOM WATERFRONT HOME IN JADE POINT SUBDIVISION! With 4 bedrooms and 4.5 baths this Sater designed home features a beautifully landscaped yard leading to an open front porch. The rear porch overlooks North Leopard Creek and your own private dock with access to some of the some of the best fishing on the East Coast. Inside you will find an extremely well built home with no expense spared in construction. Entering the front door you will notice the high ceilings, detailed trim, and expansive water views. Kitchen features include a butler's pantry, quartz countertops with granite island, Five Star gas range with stainless hood, and deep sink. The den features a stone wall gas fireplace with trey ceiling. Move to the master bedroom and take in the water views with a trey ceiling, his and her walk-in closets, and elegant master bath with garden tub, dual vanity, and tile shower. Each of the additional 2 bedroom suites on this level include their own private baths. The lower level is to be completed with an anticipated completion date for the Summer of 2024. The lower level will consist of a Kitchenette, bath, bedroom, gym, laundry closet, family room, and workshop. Square footage taken from house plans.
